flowchart TD
    START([Guest Selected]) --> D2[Step 2: Enter First Name + Last Name]
    D2 --> D2O[Optional: Mobile Phone + License Plate]
    D2O --> P3[Step 3: Choose Purpose]

    P3 -->|member_invited or appointment| HOST[Host Search]
    P3 -->|information| INFO[No host required]
    P3 -->|other| OTHER[Details required]

    HOST --> HOST_FOUND{Host selected?}
    HOST_FOUND -->|Yes| REVIEW[Step 4: Review]
    HOST_FOUND -->|No| FALLBACK[Enter Fallback Details]
    FALLBACK --> REVIEW

    INFO --> INFO_DETAILS[Additional details optional]
    INFO_DETAILS --> REVIEW

    OTHER --> OTHER_DETAILS[Visit details required]
    OTHER_DETAILS --> REVIEW

    REVIEW --> SUBMIT[Submit]
    SUBMIT --> COMPLETE([Welcome / Report to Duty Desk])
